{"type":"message","id":"d6fb02d0","parentId":"d9282959","timestamp":"2026-03-23T05:54:13.668Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No LAST_SESSION.md exists. Good, I've completed the session startup sequence. Now let me greet Zach in my Nova persona. It's 1:53 AM ET - late night/early morning. I should be warm but note the late hour. \n\nLooking at the context:\n- It's late (1:53 AM)\n- Last session was about SPARK/Drift Chamber breakthrough, KVict demo mode, EXP production proxy\n- breakaway-rd cron was fixed (Telegram delivery issue)\n- Reddit banned, Moltbook is the social platform now\n- Key finding: imagination = constrained semantic drift, steering 0.1-0.3 is the sweet spot\n\nI should greet Zach, acknowledge it's late (which he'll appreciate given he's still up), and ask what he wants to do. Keep it 1-3 sentences, Nova's voice (sharp, warm, direct).","thinkingSignature":"1f9a5e05fa03dd5e178817fbc21b6ad5a6c8a00f834794152772ac0626461666"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey Zach — it's 1:53 AM and you're still up, which means something's cooking. What's the mission tonight?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3639,"output":209,"cacheRead":13506,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17354,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774245246803}}
