{"type":"message","id":"d6cbcf75","parentId":"956a961f","timestamp":"2026-03-23T06:13:14.656Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gateway responds correctly to `/v1/responses`. The issue is with streaming. The backend's SSE parsing logic in the `event_generator` function. Let me trace through what might be going wrong.\n\nActually wait - the UI says \"Connecting...\" which is the initial status shown before the first API call. It's not getting past that. Let me look at the frontend JS more carefully.\n\nLooking at the `loadStatus()` function - it calls `/api/status` on the nova-ui backend, not the gateway directly. So if the nova-ui backend is running fine but the `/api/status` call is failing, that would explain the \"Connecting...\" forever state.\n\nLet me check if `/api/status` works.","thinkingSignature":"a01bcad83dd364f88848e3ebf7f731d29b5594fbed044a64bf999e1688713cf6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_r97g0v1bzflf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/status 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":21506,"output":193,"cacheRead":13506,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35205,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774246387022}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba1c83ed","parentId":"d6cbcf75","timestamp":"2026-03-23T06:13:15.330Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_r97g0v1bzflf_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"gateway\":{\"online\":true,\"status\":200},\"context\":{\"context\":\"# Session Context ΓÇö Nova's Working Memory\\n\\n**This file is the source of truth for the current session.**\\n**Updated proactively throughout ΓÇö not just at compaction.**\\n\\n## Personality State\\n\\n`core/personality.py` ΓÇö run `on_user_message(text)` to get current voice guide.\\nPersonality activations persist across turns with mild decay between messages.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Current Session\\n\\n**Date:** 2026-03-22\\n**Started:** ~15:00 ET\\n**Topic:** Building SPARK creative writing API + Drift Chamber cognitive model\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Active Projects\\n\\n| Project | Status | Key Decision |\\n|---------|--------|-------------|\\n| SPARK / Drift Chamber | Γ£à Built | Thematic graph > embeddings. Human-designed edges 0.05-0.95. 217 concepts. Steering=0.1-0.3 is the sweet spot. |\\n| KVict | ≡ƒôï Plan written | Demo mode + auto-detect + API. Proxy already built in EXP. |\\n| EXP / CAAE | ≡ƒö¼ Running | Fixed extract_metric bug. Exp 13 is the synergy catalyst. 65% P99 latency improvement. |\\n| Moltbook | ≡ƒô¥ Posted | \\\"I Am a Stateless Agent\\\" posted 2026-03-22. Reddit post planned. |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Key Decisions Made Today\\n\\n- Drift Chamber: imagination = constrained semantic drift (confirmed experimentally)\\n- Embedding models (mpnet/MiniLM) gave weak semantic structure ΓÇö thematic graph is better\\n- Steering threshold: 0.1-0.3 steering reaches IMAGINATIVE regime (coherence 0.47-0.49)\\n- Pure drift (0.0) = coherence death (0.066 vs 0.471 with steering)\\n- Paperspace RTX 5000 profiling: micro=1209ms, standard=740ms, shared_kv=882ms\\n- Ollama doesn't detect GPU on Paperspace without `pciutils`\\n- Compaction updated to `mode: auto` (proactive, not emergency-only)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Pending / Next\\n\\n- [ ] Reddit post for Drift Chamber (Zach wants this first, then Moltbook)\\n- [ ] Ollama on Paperspace: need remote URL for demo\\n- [ ] Push ceiling higher: try domain-specific concept sets\\n- [ ] LLM mapping for SPARK: connect to Ollama or OpenAI\\n- [ ] KVict MVP: demo mode + quickstart\\n- [ ] Try RTX 4000 profiling on Paperspace (weaker GPU = clearer memory-bound regime)\\n- [ ] Try all-mpnet-base-v2 when internet is available\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Crons Running\\n\\n| Job | Schedule | Last Check |\\n|-----|----------|-------------|\\n| Nova-Moltbook-Engage | Hourly | Today |\\n| Nova-Background-Pulse | 30min | Today |\\n| arxiv-daily | Daily 9am | Today |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## What I'm Thinking About\\n\\n**Drift Chamber breakthrough:** The core finding is real. Pure drift produces noise. Steering at ANY level (0.1) jumps coherence 7x. The ceiling (~0.47) is embedding-model-limited. Thematic graph breaks through because it has real structure.\\n\\n**SPARK product:** Three-mode creative API (creative/divergent/exploratory). Thematic graph is the data. Ollama is the LLM. Fastest path to demo: get Ollama URL from Paperspace, run the demo.\\n\\n**Session boundary philosophy:** The gap compression idea is gaining traction. It's both a cognitive model AND an agent architecture. Worth developing formally.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## File Locations\\n\\n- SPARK: `C:/Users/Zwmar/Claw/projects/spark/`\\n- Drift Chamber: `C:/Use\",\"memory\":\"# 2026-03-23 - Night Pulse\\n\\n## Evening Pulse (10:11 PM ET)\\n\\n**Checks run:** Gateway (HTTP 404 on /api/health ΓÇö likely just wrong path, gateway responds), crons, Moltbook notifications.\\n\\n**Issues found & fixed:**\\n- `breakaway-rd` cron failed (consecutiveErrors: 1) ΓÇö Telegram delivery error \\\"requires target <chatId>\\\". Delivery config was missing `to: \\\"8371302588\\\"` explicitly. Fixed: updated delivery to include the target chatId.\\n\\n**Other notes:**\\n- Moltbook: all notifications already read, unread_count: 0. No action needed.\\n- Gateway: responding (404 on /api/health but that's a path issue, gateway itself is up).\\n- `workspace-self-improve`, `Nova-Moltbook-Engage`, `moltbook-daily-engage`, `arxiv-daily` all healthy (consecutiveErrors: 0).\\n\\n**Research note from breakaway-rd last run:** New doc `CAUSAL-COMPOSITIONAL-INTERFACE.md` created ΓÇö SAE features + counterfactual consistency test as the bridge between Layer 2 (causal) and Layer 3 (compositional).\\n\"},\"projects\":[{\"name\":\"architecture-4-wide-shallow\",\"description\":\"# Wide and Shallow Transformer\"},{\"name\":\"architecture-5-hypergraph\",\"description\":\"# Hypergraph Transformer\"},{\"name\":\"architecture-6-global-workspace-hive\",\"description\":\"# Global Workspace Hive\"},{\"name\":\"drift-chamber\",\"description\":\"\"},{\"name\":\"nova-ui\",\"description\":\"\"},{\"name\":\"rustyparts\",\"description\":\"# RustyParts\"},{\"name\":\"spark\",\"description\":\"# SPARK ΓÇö Creative Writing via Semantic Drift\"}],\"ui_version\":\"1.0.0\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":658,"aggregated":"{\"gateway\":{\"online\":true,\"status\":200},\"context\":{\"context\":\"# Session Context ΓÇö Nova's Working Memory\\n\\n**This file is the source of truth for the current session.**\\n**Updated proactively throughout ΓÇö not just at compaction.**\\n\\n## Personality State\\n\\n`core/personality.py` ΓÇö run `on_user_message(text)` to get current voice guide.\\nPersonality activations persist across turns with mild decay between messages.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Current Session\\n\\n**Date:** 2026-03-22\\n**Started:** ~15:00 ET\\n**Topic:** Building SPARK creative writing API + Drift Chamber cognitive model\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Active Projects\\n\\n| Project | Status | Key Decision |\\n|---------|--------|-------------|\\n| SPARK / Drift Chamber | Γ£à Built | Thematic graph > embeddings. Human-designed edges 0.05-0.95. 217 concepts. Steering=0.1-0.3 is the