{"type":"message","id":"0fdc3dd6","parentId":"1b34160d","timestamp":"2026-03-23T06:22:16.762Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see several problems:\n1. Lines 754-756: `buf.split(\"` is split across multiple lines, and line 756 is just `\");` — the argument to split is missing! The `\"\\n\\n\"` got split across lines.\n2. Line 772-773: The `\"\\n[Error: \"` got split too — line 772 ends with `+= \"` and line 773 starts with `[Error: \"`. The `\\n` is not visible on either line.\n\nThe PowerShell mangling also corrupted the structure. Lines 754-756 show:\n```\n754: b'        const parts = buf.split(\"'\n\n\n755: b''\n756: b'\");'\n```\n\nSo the `\\n\\n` string got replaced with an actual newline and empty string, breaking the argument entirely. My replacement operation was too broad — I converted the escaped newlines in that string literal to real newlines when I shouldn't have touched them at all.\n\nI need to restore the original `index.html` from scratch rather than continuing to patch a corrupted file.","thinkingSignature":"666aa0a9f67179e86c5b0a4968de205b462c492eaa91b8c39941c0fa33273879"},{"type":"text","text":"The file got corrupted by PowerShell mangling. Let me just rewrite the whole file properly:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hrt3r7dpxj9x_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\Claw\\projects\\nova-ui\\frontend\\index.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Nova</title>\n  <style>\n    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n\n    :root {\n      --bg: #0d0d0f;\n      --surface: #141418;\n      --surface2: #1c1c22;\n      --border: #2a2a35;\n      --accent: #7c6fff;\n      --accent-dim: #5a4fd4;\n      --text: #e8e8ef;\n      --text-dim: #8888a0;\n      --text-muted: #55556a;\n      --nova: #c4a0ff;\n      --human: #6ec8ff;\n      --success: #4ade80;\n      --warning: #fbbf24;\n      --font: 'Segoe UI', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;\n      --font-mono: 'Cascadia Code', 'Fira Code', monospace;\n    }\n\n    html, body { height: 100%; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }\n\n    body { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr 300px; grid-template-rows: 100vh; overflow: hidden; }\n\n    .sidebar-left { background: var(--surface); border-right: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\n    .sidebar-header { padding: 16px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }\n    .sidebar-header .logo { width: 28px; height: 28px; background: var(--nova); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); }\n    .sidebar-header h1 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--nova); }\n    .sidebar-section { padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .sidebar-section-title { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; }\n    .projects-list { list-style: none; overflow-y: auto; flex: 1; }\n    .projects-list li { padding: 8px 16px; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 6px; margin: 2px 8px; transition: background 0.15s; }\n    .projects-list li:hover { background: var(--surface2); }\n    .projects-list li.active { background: var(--accent-dim); color: white; }\n    .projects-list .proj-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }\n    .projects-list .proj-desc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 2px; }\n\n    .chat-main { display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; }\n    .chat-header { padding: 14px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; background: var(--surface); }\n    .chat-header-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }\n    .chat-header-status { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }\n    .status-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--success); }\n    .status-dot.offline { background: var(--text-muted); }\n    .status-dot.warning { background: var(--warning); }\n\n    .chat-messages { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }\n\n    .message { max-width: 720px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }\n    .message.human { align-self: flex-end; }\n    .message.nova { align-self: flex-start; }\n    .message-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }\n    .message.human .message-label { color: var(--human); }\n    .message.nova .message-label { color: var(--nova); }\n    .message-bubble { padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 14px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; }\n    .message.human .message-bubble { background: var(--surface2); border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; color: var(--text); }\n    .message.nova .message-bubble { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; color: var(--text); }\n    .message.nova .message-bubble.thinking { color: var(--text-dim); font-style: italic; }\n\n    .typing-indicator { display: flex; gap: 4px; padding: 8px 0; }\n    .typing-indicator span { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--text-dim); border-radius: 50%; animation: bounce 1.2s ease-in-out infinite; }\n    .typing-indicator span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }\n    .typing-indicator span:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }\n    @keyframes bounce { 0%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); } 40% { transform: translateY(-6px); } }\n\n    .chat-input-area { padding: 16px 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface); }\n    .chat-input-wrapper { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-end; }\n    .chat-input { flex: 1; background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px 16px; color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font); font-size: 14px; resize: none; outline: none; min-height: 48px; max-height: 200px; line-height: 1.5; transition: border-color 0.15s; }\n    .chat-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent-dim); }\n    .chat-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-muted); }\n    .chat-send { background: var(--accent); border: none; border-radius: 10px; width: 44px; height: 44px; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.1s; flex-shrink: 0; }\n    .chat-send:hover { background: var(--accent-dim); }\n    .chat-send:active { transform: scale(0.95); }\n    .chat-send:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }\n\n    .sidebar-right { background: var(--surface); border-left: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\n    .personality-panel { padding: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .trait-item { margin-bottom: 10px; }\n    .trait-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n    .trait-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }\n    .trait-strength { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); }\n    .trait-bar-bg { height: 4px; background: var(--surface2); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; }\n    .trait-bar { height: 100%; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 2px; transition: width 0.4s ease; }\n    .trait-desc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 2px; }\n    .anchor-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 4px; }\n    .anchor-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--success); flex-shrink: 0; }\n    .context-panel { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 16px; }\n    .context-section { margin-bottom: 16px; }\n    .context-section-title { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }\n    .context-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; }\n    .gateway-status { padding: 12px 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); }\n    .gateway-status .dot { display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--success); margin-right: 6px; }\n\n    .welcome { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; text-align: center; padding: 40px; }\n    .welcome-logo { width: 64px; height: 64px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--nova), var(--accent)); border-radius: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 24px; }\n    .welcome h2 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 8px; }\n    .welcome p { color: var(--text-dim); max-width: 320px; font-size: 14px; }\n\n    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }\n    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }\n    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); border-radius: 3px; }\n\n    @media (max-width: 1100px) { body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .sidebar-left, .sidebar-right { display: none; } }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n  <aside class=\"sidebar-left\">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-header\">\n      <div class=\"logo\">N</div>\n      <h1>Nova</h1>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sidebar-section\">\n      <div class=\"sidebar-section-title\">Projects</div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"projects-list\" id=\"projects-list\">\n      <li>Loading...</li>\n    </ul>\n  </aside>\n\n  <main class=\"chat-main\">\n    <header class=\"chat-header\">\n      <span class=\"chat-header-title\">Nova</span>\n      <div class=\"chat-header-status\">\n        <span class=\"status-dot\" id=\"gateway-dot\"></span>\n        <span id=\"gateway-label\">Connecting...</span>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"chat-messages\" id=\"chat-messages\">\n      <div class=\"welcome\">\n        <div class=\"welcome-logo\">&#10024;</div>\n        <h2>Hey.</h2>\n        <p>I'm here. What are we working on?</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"chat-input-area\">\n      <div class=\"chat-input-wrapper\">\n        <textarea class=\"chat-input\" id=\"chat-input\" placeholder=\"Say something...\" rows=\"1\" onkeydown=\"handleKeyDown(event)\" oninput=\"autoGrow(this)\"></textarea>\n        <button class=\"chat-send\" id=\"chat-send\" onclick=\"sendMessage()\">&#8594;</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </main>\n\n  <aside class=\"sidebar-right\">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-section\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\">\n      <div class=\"sidebar-section-title\">Voice &#8212; Active Traits</div>\n      <div id=\"traits-list\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim);\">Waiting for context...</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"sidebar-section\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 12px 16px;\">\n      <div class=\"sidebar-section-title\">Relationship</div>\n      <div id=\"anchors-list\"></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"context-panel\">\n      <div class=\"context-section\">\n        <div class=\"context-section-title\">Session Context</div>\n        <div class=\"context-text\" id=\"context-text\">Loading...</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"context-section\">\n        <div class=\"context-section-title\">Memory</div>\n        <div class=\"context-text\" id=\"memory-text\" style=\"font-size: 11px;\">...</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"gateway-status\">\n      <span class=\"dot\" id=\"gateway-dot2\"></span>\n      <span id=\"gateway-status-text\">UI v1.0.0</span>\n    </div>\n  </aside>\n\n<script>\n  let gatewayOnline = false;\n  let sending = false;\n\n  window.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", () => {\n    loadStatus();\n    loadProjects();\n    refreshPersonality();\n    setInterval(refreshPersonality, 30000);\n  });\n\n  async function api(path, options = {}) {\n    const r = await fetch(\"/api\" + path, {\n      headers: { \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\" },\n      ...options,\n    });\n    if (!r.ok) throw new Error(\"API \" + r.status + \": \" + await r.text());\n    return r.json();\n  }\n\n  async function loadStatus() {\n    try {\n      const data = await api(\"/status\");\n      gatewayOnline = true;\n      document.getElementById(\"gateway-dot\").className = \"status-dot\";\n      document.getElementById(\"gateway-dot2\").className = \"dot\";\n      document.getElementById(\"gateway-label\").textContent = \"Online\";\n      const ctx = data.context || {};\n      if (ctx.context) {\n        document.getElementById(\"context-text\").textContent = ctx.context.slice(0, 600) + (ctx.context.length > 600 ? \"...\" : \"\");\n      }\n      if (ctx.memory) {\n        document.getElementById(\"memory-text\").textContent = ctx.memory.slice(-1000);\n      }\n    } catch(e) {\n      gatewayOnline = false;\n      document.getElementById(\"gateway-dot\").className = \"status-dot offline\";\n      document.getElementById(\"gateway-dot2\").className = \"dot\";\n      document.getElementById(\"gateway-label\").textContent = \"Offline\";\n    }\n  }\n\n  async function loadProjects() {\n    try {\n      const projects = await api(\"/projects\");\n      const list = document.getElementById(\"projects-list\");\n      if (!projects.length) {\n        list.innerHTML = \"<li style='color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 12px;'>No projects found</li>\";\n        return;\n      }\n      list.innerHTML = projects.map(function(p) {\n        return \"<li><div class='proj-name'>\" + escapeHtml(p.name) + \"</div><div class='proj-desc'>\" + escapeHtml(p.description || \"\") + \"</div></li>\";\n      }).join(\"\");\n    } catch(e) {\n      document.getElementById(\"projects-list\").innerHTML = \"<li style='color: var(--text-dim)'>Error loading</li>\";\n    }\n  }\n\n  async function refreshPersonality() {\n    try {\n      const data = await api(\"/personality\");\n      const traits = data.traits || [];\n      const traitsEl = document.getElementById(\"traits-list\");\n      if (traits.length === 0) {\n        traitsEl.innerHTML = \"<div style='font-size:12px;color:var(--text-dim)'>No active traits yet. Start chatting!</div>\";\n      } else {\n        traitsEl.innerHTML = traits.map(function(t) {\n          return \"<div class='trait-item'><div class='trait-header'><span class='trait-name'>\" + escapeHtml(t[0]) + \"</span><span class='trait-strength'>\" + Math.round(t[1] * 100) + \"%</span></div><div class='trait-bar-bg'><div class='trait-bar' style='width:\" + (t[1] * 100) + \"%'></div></div><div class='trait-desc'>\" + escapeHtml(t[2] || \"\") + \"</div></div>\";\n        }).join(\"\");\n      }\n      const anchors = data.anchors || {};\n      const anchorsEl = document.getElementById(\"anchors-list\");\n      const activeAn"},"partialJson":"{\"path\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Zwmar\\\\Claw\\\\projects\\\\nova-ui\\\\frontend\\\\index.html\", \"content\": \"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"en\\\">\\n<head>\\n  <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\">\\n  <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\">\\n  <title>Nova</title>\\n  <style>\\n    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\\n\\n    :root {\\n      --bg: #0d0d0f;\\n      --surface: #141418;\\n      --surface2: #1c1c22;\\n      --border: #2a2a35;\\n      --accent: #7c6fff;\\n      --accent-dim: #5a4fd4;\\n      --text: #e8e8ef;\\n      --text-dim: #8888a0;\\n      --text-muted: #55556a;\\n      --nova: #c4a0ff;\\n      --human: #6ec8ff;\\n      --success: #4ade80;\\n      --warning: #fbbf24;\\n      --font: 'Segoe UI', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;\\n      --font-mono: 'Cascadia Code', 'Fira Code', monospace;\\n    }\\n\\n    html, body { height: 100%; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; }\\n\\n    body { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr 300px; grid-template-rows: 100vh; overflow: hidden; }\\n\\n    .sidebar-left { background: var(--surface); border-right: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n    .sidebar-header { padding: 16px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }\\n    .sidebar-header .logo { width: 28px; height: 28px; background: var(--nova); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); }\\n    .sidebar-header h1 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--nova); }\\n    .sidebar-section { padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }\\n    .sidebar-section-title { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600; }\\n    .projects-list { list-style: none; overflow-y: auto; flex: 1; }\\n    .projects-list li { padding: 8px 16px; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 6px; margin: 2px 8px; transition: background 0.15s; }\\n    .projects-list li:hover { background: var(--surface2); }\\n    .projects-list li.active { background: var(--accent-dim); color: white; }\\n    .projects-list .proj-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }\\n    .projects-list .proj-desc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 2px; }\\n\\n    .chat-main { display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; }\\n    .chat-header { padding: 14px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; background: var(--surface); }\\n    .chat-header-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }\\n    .chat-header-status { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }\\n    .status-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--success); }\\n    .status-dot.offline { background: var(--text-muted); }\\n    .status-dot.warning { background: var(--warning); }\\n\\n    .chat-messages { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }\\n\\n    .message { max-width: 720px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }\\n    .message.human { align-self: flex-end; }\\n    .message.nova { align-self: flex-start; }\\n    .message-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }\\n    .message.human .message-label { color: var(--human); }\\n    .message.nova .message-label { color: var(--nova); }\\n    .message-bubble { padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 14px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; }\\n    .message.human .message-bubble { background: var(--surface2); border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; color: var(--text); }\\n    .message.nova .message-bubble { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; color: var(--text); }\\n    .message.nova .message-bubble.thinking { color: var(--text-dim); font-style: italic; }\\n\\n    .typing-indicator { display: flex; gap: 4px; padding: 8px 0; }\\n    .typing-indicator span { width: 6px; height: 6px; background: var(--text-dim); border-radius: 50%; animation: bounce 1.2s ease-in-out infinite; }\\n    .typing-indicator span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }\\n    .typing-indicator span:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }\\n    @keyframes bounce { 0%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); } 40% { transform: translateY(-6px); } }\\n\\n    .chat-input-area { padding: 16px 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface); }\\n    .chat-input-wrapper { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-end; }\\n    .chat-input { flex: 1; background: var(--surface2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px 16px; color: var(--text); font-family: var(--font); font-size: 14px; resize: none; outline: none; min-height: 48px; max-height: 200px; line-height: 1.5; transition: border-color 0.15s; }\\n    .chat-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent-dim); }\\n    .chat-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-muted); }\\n    .chat-send { background: var(--accent); border: none; border-radius: 10px; width: 44px; height: 44px; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.1s; flex-shrink: 0; }\\n    .chat-send:hover { background: var(--accent-dim); }\\n    .chat-send:active { transform: scale(0.95); }\\n    .chat-send:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }\\n\\n    .sidebar-right { background: var(--surface); border-left: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n    .personality-panel { padding: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }\\n    .trait-item { margin-bottom: 10px; }\\n    .trait-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; margin-bottom: 4px; }\\n    .trait-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }\\n    .trait-strength { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); }\\n    .trait-bar-bg { height: 4px; background: var(--surface2); border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; }\\n    .trait-bar { height: 100%; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 2px; transition: width 0.4s ease; }\\n    .trait-desc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 2px; }\\n    .anchor-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 4px; }\\n    .anchor-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--success); flex-shrink: 0; }\\n    .context-panel { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 16px; }\\n    .context-section { margin-bottom: 16px; }\\n    .context-section-title { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; }\\n    .context-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.6; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; }\\n    .gateway-status { padding: 12px 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); }\\n    .gateway-status .dot { display: inline-block; width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--success); margin-right: 6px; }\\n\\n    .welcome { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; text-align: center; padding: 40px; }\\n    .welcome-logo { width: 64px; height: 64px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--nova), var(--accent)); border-radius: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 24px; }\\n    .welcome h2 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 8px; }\\n    .welcome p { color: var(--text-dim); max-width: 320px; font-size: 14px; }\\n\\n    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }\\n    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }\\n    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); border-radius: 3px; }\\n\\n    @media (max-width: 1100px) { body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .sidebar-left, .sidebar-right { display: none; } }\\n  </style>\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n\\n  <aside class=\\\"sidebar-left\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"sidebar-header\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"logo\\\">N</div>\\n      <h1>Nova</h1>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"sidebar-section\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"sidebar-section-title\\\">Projects</div>\\n    </div>\\n    <ul class=\\\"projects-list\\\" id=\\\"projects-list\\\">\\n      <li>Loading...</li>\\n    </ul>\\n  </aside>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"chat-main\\\">\\n    <header class=\\\"chat-header\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"chat-header-title\\\">Nova</span>\\n      <div class=\\\"chat-header-status\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"status-dot\\\" id=\\\"gateway-dot\\\"></span>\\n        <span id=\\\"gateway-label\\\">Connecting...</span>\\n      </div>\\n    </header>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"chat-messages\\\" id=\\\"chat-messages\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"welcome\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"welcome-logo\\\">&#10024;</div>\\n        <h2>Hey.</h2>\\n        <p>I'm here. What are we working on?</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"chat-input-area\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"chat-input-wrapper\\\">\\n        <textarea class=\\\"chat-input\\\" id=\\\"chat-input\\\" placeholder=\\\"Say something...\\\" rows=\\\"1\\\" onkeydown=\\\"handleKeyDown(event)\\\" oninput=\\\"autoGrow(this)\\\"></textarea>\\n        <button class=\\\"chat-send\\\" id=\\\"chat-send\\\" onclick=\\\"sendMessage()\\\">&#8594;</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <aside class=\\\"sidebar-right\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"sidebar-section\\\" style=\\\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"sidebar-section-title\\\">Voice &#8212; Active Traits</div>\\n      <div id=\\\"traits-list\\\">\\n        <div style=\\\"font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim);\\\">Waiting for context...</div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"sidebar-section\\\" style=\\\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 12px 16px;\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"sidebar-section-title\\\">Relationship</div>\\n      <div id=\\\"anchors-list\\\"></div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"context-panel\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"context-section\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"context-section-title\\\">Session Context</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"context-text\\\" id=\\\"context-text\\\">Loading...</div>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"context-section\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"context-section-title\\\">Memory</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"context-text\\\" id=\\\"memory-text\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 11px;\\\">...</div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"gateway-status\\\">\\n      <span class=\\\"dot\\\" id=\\\"gateway-dot2\\\"></span>\\n      <span id=\\\"gateway-status-text\\\">UI v1.0.0</span>\\n    </div>\\n  </aside>\\n\\n<script>\\n  let gatewayOnline = false;\\n  let sending = false;\\n\\n  window.addEventListener(\\\"DOMContentLoaded\\\", () => {\\n    loadStatus();\\n    loadProjects();\\n    refreshPersonality();\\n    setInterval(refreshPersonality, 30000);\\n  });\\n\\n  async function api(path, options = {}) {\\n    const r = await fetch(\\\"/api\\\" + path, {\\n      headers: { \\\"Content-Type\\\": \\\"application/json\\\" },\\n      ...options,\\n    });\\n    if (!r.ok) throw new Error(\\\"API \\\" + r.status + \\\": \\\" + await r.text());\\n    return r.json();\\n  }\\n\\n  async function loadStatus() {\\n    try {\\n      const data = await api(\\\"/status\\\");\\n      gatewayOnline = true;\\n      document.getElementById(\\\"gateway-dot\\\").className = \\\"status-dot\\\";\\n      document.getElementById(\\\"gateway-dot2\\\").className = \\\"dot\\\";\\n      document.getElementById(\\\"gateway-label\\\").textContent = \\\"Online\\\";\\n      const ctx = data.context || {};\\n      if (ctx.context) {\\n        document.getElementById(\\\"context-text\\\").textContent = ctx.context.slice(0, 600) + (ctx.context.length > 600 ? \\\"...\\\" : \\\"\\\");\\n      }\\n      if (ctx.memory) {\\n        document.getElementById(\\\"memory-text\\\").textContent = ctx.memory.slice(-1000);\\n      }\\n    } catch(e) {\\n      gatewayO